articles.title: India vs Australia 2nd T20 match prediction: Who’ll win IND vs AUS match? Fantasy team, pitch report and more | Mint - Mint
articles.description: India and Australia will take on each other on November 26 at the Greenfield International Stadium in Thiruvananthapuram. The Men in Blue are leading the series 1-0.
